### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST SUPPLIERS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@warehouseToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### ============================================
### 🏢 2. GET ALL SUPPLIERS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All Suppliers (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get Suppliers with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Search Suppliers by Keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers?keyword=Cong
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 No Token - Get Suppliers (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET SUPPLIER BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get Supplier by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Admin - Get Non-existent Supplier (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ➕ 4. CREATE SUPPLIER
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Create Supplier Success (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Công ty TNHH Test Supplier",
  "phone": "02812345678",
  "email": "supplier@test.com",
  "address": "123 Đường Test, Quận 1, TP.HCM"
}

### 4.2 Admin - Create Supplier without Name (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "phone": "02812345679"
}

### 4.3 Admin - Create Supplier with Duplicate Name (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Công ty TNHH Test Supplier",
  "phone": "02812345680"
}

### 4.4 Admin - Create Supplier with Duplicate Phone (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Another Supplier",
  "phone": "02812345678"
}

### ============================================
### ✏️ 5. UPDATE SUPPLIER
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Update Supplier (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Supplier Name",
  "phone": "02898765432",
  "email": "updated@supplier.com",
  "address": "456 Đường Mới, Quận 2, TP.HCM",
  "isActive": true
}

### 5.2 Admin - Update Non-existent Supplier (Expected: 404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Non Existent Supplier"
}

### 5.3 Admin - Deactivate Supplier
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

### ============================================
### 🗑️ 6. DELETE SUPPLIER
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Delete Supplier (Expected: 200 OK - nếu không có đơn đặt hàng)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Admin - Delete Supplier with Purchase Orders (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.3 Admin - Delete Non-existent Supplier (Expected: 404 Not Found)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📦 7. GET SUPPLIER PRODUCTS
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Get Supplier Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Admin - Get Supplier Products with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.3 Admin - Get Products for Non-existent Supplier (Expected: 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/99999/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🔎 8. QUICK SEARCH SUPPLIERS
### ============================================

### 8.1 Quick Search by Name (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/search/quick?keyword=Cong
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Quick Search by Phone (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/search/quick?keyword=028
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.3 Quick Search - Short Keyword (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/search/quick?keyword=a
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến @adminToken, @managerToken
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
### ============================================
### ✅ CHECKLIST TEST
### ============================================
### 
### GET ALL:
### [ ] Admin get all suppliers → 200 OK
### [ ] Admin get with pagination → 200 OK
### [ ] Admin search suppliers → 200 OK
### [ ] No token → 401 Unauthorized
###
### GET BY ID:
### [ ] Get existing supplier → 200 OK
### [ ] Get non-existent supplier → 404 Not Found
###
### CREATE:
### [ ] Create valid supplier → 200 OK
### [ ] Create without name → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create duplicate name → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create duplicate phone → 400 Bad Request
###
### UPDATE:
### [ ] Update existing supplier → 200 OK
### [ ] Update non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Deactivate supplier → 200 OK
###
### DELETE:
### [ ] Delete supplier without POs → 200 OK
### [ ] Delete supplier with POs → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Delete non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### SUPPLIER PRODUCTS:
### [ ] Get supplier products → 200 OK
### [ ] Get products with pagination → 200 OK
### [ ] Get products non-existent supplier → 404
###
### QUICK SEARCH:
### [ ] Search by name → 200 OK
### [ ] Search by phone → 200 OK
### [ ] Search short keyword → 400 Bad Request
###